{"tid":954574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真討論]瑪利亞是否臭雞？","createTime":"2018-12-24T16:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T15:30:39.000Z","uid":225636,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dba1e3734715e662636724d39483285a54d48b8a","tid":954574,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n我以一個普通人嘅諗法去講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一個可能<br />\n未婚懷孕，派完帽就想搵人賣單<br />\n仲呃尻條仔話係上天嘅恩賜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一隻講大話唔眨眼嘅臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二個可能<br />\n當佢俾人屌完都唔知，毫無性知識。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一隻蠢到抵俾人屌嘅臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反觀，<br />\n<br />\n條仔(唔知佢叫乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )連咁屎嘅大話都相信，仲要養埋個便宜仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到頭來只係痴心換絕情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係真愛都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當今世上，最廣為人知嘅兵非佢莫屬<br />\n<br />\n啊邊個，叫住你做兵王先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你嘅情操絕對值得天下人嘅尊重。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有機會同你講一句，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中出即飛瑪利亞隻臭雞啦！<br />\nYou Deserve Better！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">瑪利亞你隻臭雞！<br />\n落地獄啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91758d730ccb0638a4f96642a8c4815e9adffab4","tid":954574,"uid":9766,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:37:58.000Z","msg":"冇隻臭雞你撚有假放咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c5d8d55532d60b9b9973c2a1ff61efa6af992e","tid":954574,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91758d730ccb0638a4f96642a8c4815e9adffab4","tid":954574,"uid":9766,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:37:58.000Z","msg":"冇隻臭雞你撚有假放咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"將心比己<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老婆晚晚俾人中出<br />\n換黎多一日假期<br />\n你又制唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204e072874bc2e184f619f17fc7b2e76ccfb1d56","tid":954574,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:09:03.000Z","msg":"希望有人為瑪利亞平反<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n值明啊邊個嘅決定係冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c969b1631a42e899dc3568f6e79ce4698faa9ed","tid":954574,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦你！<br />\n質疑我嘅聖母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6589619c2bb4cf1ff93c26fa7524fbbf14f07451","tid":954574,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c969b1631a42e899dc3568f6e79ce4698faa9ed","tid":954574,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦你！<br />\n質疑我嘅聖母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"冇錯 佢係聖母<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁佢係唔係臭雞？"},{"pid":"9144bfc4a